{"tid":495843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加班文化嚴重　日企研無人機播音樂促員工回家","createTime":"2017-12-11T06:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T07:42:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"02c6a0f27d42e619a7f86e9f7282fb5c3d7b41db","tid":495843,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171211/s00005/a7357f8df63250152895fcc07c0eeddb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171211%2Fs00005%2Fa7357f8df63250152895fcc07c0eeddb.jpg&h=ce802448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本加班文化嚴重，長期超時工作令不少人身心俱疲。有日本公司研發一部「懂唱歌」的無人機，當它發現有員工在下班時間後仍在辦公室工作，會播放音樂令他下班回家。<br />\n<br />\n無人機名為「T-Frend」，在員工下班後，會按預先設定的路線巡視辦公室。若偵測到有人加班，無人機便會在該員工身旁徘徊，並播放蘇格蘭民歌「友誼地久天長」（Auld Lang Syne）。在日本，這歌通常用以表示商店即將關門。<br />\n<br />\n無人機由大成建設、電訊公司NTT East和無人機開發公司Blue Innovation共同研發，計劃在明年4月推出，預計收費是每月50萬日圓（約34,464港元）。公司亦正研發無人機的面部識別技術，用以分辨誰人在下班後仍在辦公室。<br />\n<br />\n在日本，長時間工作被視為忠誠和願意奉獻的表現，政府一直嘗試改變這種加班文化。在今年2月，政府推行「Premium Friday」計劃，呼籲員工在每月最後一個星期五提早下班，希望能夠減少工時。不過計劃的反應一般，很多人指出，每月最後一個星期五是最忙碌的日子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171211/s00005/1512969066661\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171211%2Fs00005%2F1512969066661&d=K3Mti2WBIh1zTkKWbeZO7JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=89e88e48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171211%2Fs00005%2F1512969066661&h=1986d6b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171211/s00005/1512969066661</a>"},{"pid":"363d2bbcd2860a61049fd72a78a88b96e607c276","tid":495843,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:22:58.000Z","msg":"戴面具開OT"},{"pid":"9eeb15ab89f8b24d11bd8e98cd9d4a2227fecf6d","tid":495843,"uid":66494,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:38:57.000Z","msg":"香港就用無人機睇你有無乖乖地加班"},{"pid":"8da5f381476093070ffc648e1a57d16d8c261eda","tid":495843,"uid":26506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:43:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港就用無人機睇你有無乖乖地加班</blockquote><br />\n傻啦無人機都唔會買吖"},{"pid":"65d2489b93c672567ecf5d5c588e2342297fd996","tid":495843,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:44:58.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e38a30368f49816e0aca85e1e59f1ed179fea70","tid":495843,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:55:05.000Z","msg":"お帰りましょう。"},{"pid":"56c0aa24d599f18e9da7f0593e06e4d27d87637f","tid":495843,"uid":13450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:24:54.000Z","msg":"你真係唔想佢OT<br />\n可以set死系統 登出佢電腦 CUT上網<br />\nCUT電話 咁佢咪會返歸<br />\n香港有企業係咁做 不過12點先CUT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85b3b7dc5354bfefef042725828f8c4ff2799b0","tid":495843,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:25:20.000Z","msg":"how about請多d人手/炒撚哂d老屎忽？"},{"pid":"94ac652838724f30acb0b2ce3ddba169d2a37ea1","tid":495843,"uid":39463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港有office 8pm強制熄機<br />\n結果就係個個用notebook OT"},{"pid":"6f782c5c3d86a5aea81f1b95a8078a0d2918effa","tid":495843,"uid":33463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"香港加班係自願架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bd58cee0ed636e08ea43601720164c5c2df8a7","tid":495843,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:28:17.000Z","msg":"戴耳塞， 我諗除非搵黑社會 邊個加班打佢老闆 咁先有用"},